      "content": "i hear you, but it feels like you're saying one side is just a \"myth\" used by politicians while the other side is the only actual truth. isn't it possible for both perspectives to have merit in different contexts, or are you saying the \"deterrence\" argument is just objectively wrong and not even a valid sociological perspective anymore?",
